<P><UL>
<H1> 
Why Multimedia Project Management ?</UL></P>
</H1> 
<P><UL>
Substantial effort in measuring traditional transaction processing & process control systems , little effort in determining and evaluating project management of MSS
</UL><UL>

</UL><UL>
<LI>Unique software - need for storyboarding early in the development cycle
</UL><UL>
<LI>Tools & Techniques specific to multimedia
</UL><UL>
<LI>Different emphasis of project management - managers from diverse background as opposed to mangers in software projects
</UL><UL>
<LI>Cross disciplinary teams
</UL><UL>
<LI>Inherently different nature media of multimedia systems
</UL><UL>

</UL><UL>

</UL><UL>
Direct application of existing models and measures may not meet management needs  in development of MSS
</UL></P>
